name: Unidentified_Grysk_outrider_1
content:
Around 18 BBY, a Grysk who had been told to not be present with other Grysk forces at a mine on the Unknown Regions planet Sunrise by the Grysk operative Jixtus approached Pathfinder navigator Qilori. They told Qilori to take a message to Jixtus with another Grysk: that if the operative signaled them to do so, they would sow chaos and reap death among his enemies, as well as bring him the one. A Paccosh then ordered Qilori to go to his barracks at a camp, and Qilori left. The navigator later told Jixtus that the two Grysks had eluded the Paccian slaughter.
The Grysk outrider appeared in the 2021 novel Thrawn Ascendancy: Lesser Evil, the final volume in Timothy Zahn's Ascendancy Trilogy.
